text: Oluwatobi Antigha (born March 16, 1993) is a professional Canadian football linebacker and defensive lineman for the Winnipeg Blue Bombers of the Canadian Football League (CFL). He played college football for the Presbyterian Blue Hose. ==Professional career== Antigha played for two seasons with the Saskatchewan Roughriders before joining the Toronto Argonauts as a free agent on February 13, 2019.
